        "ggBtYilx_f5_text": "<p>Last updated: <span style=\"color:#575757;\"><strong>April 2024</strong></span></p>",
        "ggOL9pOVBNP_text": "<p>Our refund policy is designed to ensure customer satisfaction. If for any reason you are not satisfied with your purchase, you can request a refund within a certain timeframe.&nbsp;</p>",
